title.en: Kurotou no Nemureru Majutsushi Toraware no Musume to Shirarezaru Kinjutsu
Imouto ni Konyakusha wo Toraretara, Juuna Ouji ni Kyuukon saremashita
Konyaku Haki Sareta Kaedama Reijou, Hatsukoi no Toshiue Ouji ni Dekiai Sareru
Zense Seijo datta Watashi wa Kusushi ni narimashita
Tsuihousareta Moto Reijou, Mori de Hirotta Ouji ni Dekiaisare Seijo ni Mezameru
Konyaku Haki wa Honmou desu! Seijo no Chikara ga Kaika Shita no de Watashi wa Jiyuu ni Kurashimasu - Honmono no Seijou wa Gishi de wa Naku Watashi deshita
Kyou kara Akujo ni narimasu! Tsukaisute no Migawari Seijo Nante Gomen desu
Boukun na Ane ni Suteraretara, Koushaku Kakka ni Hirowaremashita
Fukigen na Koushaku-sama wa Uso Hakkenki Tsuki Reijou no Torisetsu wo Goshomou desu
Kao Dake Seijo na no ni, Shi ni Modottara Reikoku Datta Koushaku-sama no Hon'ne ga Ama Sugimasu!
Ane no Migawari de Konyaku shitara Naze ka Henkyou no Seijo to Yobareru you ni narimashita
Cheat Shoujo ga Boukun Seiou ni Dekiai saresou desu ga, Ima wa Mahou ni Muchuu nan desu!!!
Akuyaku Reijou no Kyouji - Konyakusha wo Ubaitotte Gishi wo Oidashita Watashi wa, Douyara Ima kara Hametsu suru you desu
